- <i>Calling Ruby.</i>

07:35.890 --> 07:37.425
[phone line ringing]

07:37.625 --> 07:38.592
[Ruby on voicemail]
<i>Hey, it's Ruby.</i>

07:38.726 --> 07:39.794
<i>Leave me a message</i>

07:39.927 --> 07:41.562
<i>and I might call you back.</i>

07:47.702 --> 07:49.637
[intense music]

07:57.211 --> 07:58.746
[sniffles]

08:02.149 --> 08:03.351
Call Ruby.

08:03.751 --> 08:07.054
[automated voice]
<i>Calling Ruby.</i>

08:07.188 --> 08:08.956
<i>[Ruby on voicemail] Hey,</i>
<i>it's Ruby, leave me a message</i>

08:09.090 --> 08:10.925
<i>and I might call you back.</i>

08:11.525 --> 08:13.327
[breathing heavily]

08:13.661 --> 08:14.695
[coughs]

08:14.829 --> 08:16.330
Hey, Ruby, I um...

08:16.464 --> 08:17.965
know about...

08:19.767 --> 08:22.470
I went to your school today
to try and find you.

08:22.603 --> 08:27.742
And I saw your friend Sarah
and she...

08:32.679 --> 08:35.549
[sniffles]
I uh, I saw the picture.

08:36.650 --> 08:38.184
It's not your fault.

08:38.986 --> 08:40.221
Okay?

08:42.023 --> 08:45.893
[sobs] I just... I just really
want to hear your voice.

08:46.560 --> 08:49.030
[sniffles] Okay? Uh, just...

08:49.864 --> 08:51.198
Just please call me. Call me.

08:51.332 --> 08:53.667
Call me before
you do anything, okay?

08:54.235 --> 08:55.603
[phone beeps]

09:00.241 --> 09:01.742
[phone ringing]

09:01.876 --> 09:03.844
[automated voice]
