09:03.978 --> 09:05.312
Ignore.

09:07.214 --> 09:08.416
[phone ringing]

09:08.549 --> 09:09.984
-Ignore!
- <i>Incoming call...</i>

09:10.117 --> 09:11.585
Fuck off, Benny.

09:14.422 --> 09:15.923
[phone ringing]

09:16.057 --> 09:17.526
[automated voice]
<i>Incoming call from Terri.</i>

09:17.658 --> 09:19.260
Answer. Fuck.
Did you know, Terri?

09:19.427 --> 09:21.095
- <i>The cops are calling me.</i>
-Did you know what he was doing?

09:21.228 --> 09:22.797
Did you know what's happening
in your house?

09:22.930 --> 09:24.698
<i>They said you took Ruby,</i>
<i>are you insane?</i>

09:24.865 --> 09:26.567
-In your fucking house, Terri!
<i>-...you're not drinking again!</i>

09:26.700 --> 09:28.369
Fuck you Terri!
You know I don't drink.

09:28.503 --> 09:30.404
[Terri] <i>I don't know anything</i>
<i>about you Tom,</i>

09:30.539 --> 09:31.939
<i>and I don't want to know!</i>

09:32.106 --> 09:33.707
<i>You promised to stay away,</i>
<i>remember?</i>

09:33.841 --> 09:35.009
- <i>That was the deal!</i>
-Oh no, Terri!

09:35.142 --> 09:36.811
That was your fucking deal!

09:36.944 --> 09:38.212
[Terri] <i>Is this your way</i>
<i>of getting back at me?</i>

09:38.513 --> 09:40.448
<i>Bring her back okay?</i>
<i>Bring my daughter back.</i>

09:40.581 --> 09:42.883
- <i>Will you do that, please?</i>
-I don't... I don't have her!

09:43.017 --> 09:45.186
-Listen to me!
- <i>No, you listen!</i>

09:45.352 --> 09:47.054
<i>[Terri] The police told me</i>
<i>someone saw a man</i>

09:47.188 --> 09:48.956
<i>put a girl into a truck</i>
<i>outside of my house.</i>

09:49.090 --> 09:50.525
<i>-And it sure as shit...</i>
-What?

09:50.658 --> 09:52.393
[Terri]
<i>...sounds like your truck, Tom!</i>

09:53.027 --> 09:54.728
Well, it's not my fucking
truck, is it?

09:54.862 --> 09:56.730
<i>I'm driving home,</i>
<i>I'm almost at my house</i>

09:56.864 --> 09:58.332
<i>and the cops are already there.</i>

09:58.466 --> 10:00.434
<i>If you're drinking,</i>
<i>put Ruby in a cab.</i>

10:00.569 --> 10:02.203
<i>Do it now.</i>
<i>I mean it!</i>

10:02.336 --> 10:04.338
Terri, don't go home!
Terri don't...

10:04.472 --> 10:06.941
[sobs]
...go home.

10:07.174 --> 10:11.612
[sobbing] No.
Don't go home.

10:11.812 --> 10:13.614
Please, don't go home.

10:14.315 --> 10:16.016
[sobbing]

10:16.551 --> 10:18.786
[breathing heavily]

10:21.655 --> 10:23.891
[windshield squeaking]

10:29.864 --> 10:32.099
[whirring]

10:47.915 --> 10:50.151
[intense music]

11:02.163 --> 11:03.797
Oh, fuck.

11:13.807 --> 11:15.510
<i>-Incoming call from Terri.</i>
-Answer!

11:15.644 --> 11:16.744
[Terri]
<i>He's dead!</i>

11:16.877 --> 11:18.245
<i>You killed him!</i>

11:18.379 --> 11:19.813
<i>Oh, my God!</i>
<i>What have you done?</i>

11:19.980 --> 11:22.283
<i>He's dead, you fucking psycho!</i>

11:22.449 --> 11:23.951
<i>What have you done?</i>

11:24.118 --> 11:26.420
<i>He's dead!</i>
<i>Oh, bring my daughter back!</i>

11:26.555 --> 11:27.755
[phone beeps]

11:27.888 --> 11:29.658
[engine idling]

11:29.790 --> 11:32.026
[insects chirping]

11:36.297 --> 11:38.332
[dramatic music]

11:49.310 --> 11:50.477
[phone ringing]

11:50.645 --> 11:51.946
[automated voice]
<i>Incoming call from</i>

11:52.079 --> 11:54.014
<i>Emergency Services.</i>

11:54.215 --> 11:55.449
Ignore.

11:57.384 --> 11:58.786
[phone ringing]

11:58.919 --> 11:59.853
[automated voice]
<i>Incoming call from</i>

11:59.987 --> 12:01.255
<i>Emergency Services.</i>

12:01.388 --> 12:02.856
Ignore.

12:06.727 --> 12:08.262
[phone ringing]

12:08.395 --> 12:10.998
[automated voice]
<i>Incoming call from Unknown.</i>

12:11.600 --> 12:12.967
[phone ringing]

12:14.034 --> 12:15.704
Ruby?
Answer!

12:15.903 --> 12:17.071
Ruby!

12:17.438 --> 12:19.206
-[The Associate] <i>Mr. Roth.</i>
-Fuck.

12:19.373 --> 12:20.874
[The Associate]
<i>Thank you for taking my call.</i>

12:21.008 --> 12:22.443
Yeah look, uh, this isn't
a good time.

12:22.577 --> 12:23.978
So just, you call the office

12:24.111 --> 12:25.614
and Trudy will, uh,
sort you out. Alright?

12:25.746 --> 12:27.181
[phone beeps]

12:27.515 --> 12:29.149
[truck rumbling]

12:32.987 --> 12:34.556
Check messages.

12:35.089 --> 12:36.725
[automated voice]
<i>You have two new messages</i>

12:36.857 --> 12:38.425
<i>and one saved message.</i>

12:38.593 --> 12:41.295
<i>First new message</i>
<i>received today.</i>

12:41.495 --> 12:43.430
<i>6:56 p.m.</i>

12:45.266 --> 12:46.967
[Benny on phone]
<i>Yeah, hi, it's Benny.</i>

12:47.101 --> 12:49.638
<i>Answer your fucking phone</i>
<i>fuck-knuckle!</i>

12:50.104 --> 12:51.673
<i>What did I tell you</i>
<i>two days ago?</i>

12:51.839 --> 12:54.475
<i>Sort out that cracked seam weld</i>
<i>on the fucking flare stack.</i>

12:54.609 --> 12:57.278
<i>I can smell the bloody gas</i>
<i>all the way from Mercy Road.</i>

12:57.444 --> 12:59.748
-[Benny] <i>Fucking cunt.</i>
-[Tom] Delete.

12:59.880 --> 13:01.382
[automated voice]
<i>Message deleted.</i>

13:01.549 --> 13:02.751
<i>Second new message.</i>

13:02.883 --> 13:05.486
<i>Received today, 6:59 p.m.</i>

13:05.754 --> 13:06.920
[Abigail]
<i>Hello, Mr. Roth.</i>

13:07.087 --> 13:08.757
<i>My name is Abigail Peterson</i>

13:08.889 --> 13:10.725
<i>from the State Protection Unit.</i>

13:10.991 --> 13:12.860
<i>I'm a crisis negotiator.</i>

13:13.728 --> 13:15.730
<i>I know you're dealing with</i>
<i>a lot of stress</i>

13:15.863 --> 13:17.732
<i>and confusion right now.</i>

13:18.299 --> 13:21.101
<i>I want to assure you</i>
<i>our single goal at this time</i>

13:21.235 --> 13:24.238
<i>is to ensure the safety</i>
<i>of your daughter, Ruby.</i>

13:24.639 --> 13:26.574
<i>We just need to know</i>
<i>she's alright.</i>

13:26.741 --> 13:28.942
<i>Now I think it's best</i>
<i>if you bring her back</i>

13:29.109 --> 13:32.514
<i>so we can help you make</i>
<i>sense of what's happened here.</i>

13:33.314 --> 13:35.949
<i>We need to know</i>
<i>that Ruby is alright, Tom.</i>

13:36.083 --> 13:38.586
<i>So please call me back</i>
<i>at this number.</i>

13:38.886 --> 13:40.154
[Tom]
Delete.

13:40.321 --> 13:42.289
[automated voice]
<i>Message deleted.</i>

13:47.995 --> 13:50.030
[tires squealing]

13:52.734 --> 13:54.168
[handbrake cranks]

13:55.969 --> 13:58.205
[heavy breathing]

13:59.674 --> 14:01.909
[engine idling]

14:03.944 --> 14:05.846
Sarah.

14:06.748 --> 14:08.182
Call Sarah.

14:08.315 --> 14:10.552
[automated voice]
<i>Calling Sarah Waters.</i>

14:12.186 --> 14:14.421
[phone line ringing]

14:18.258 --> 14:19.893
Sarah, it's Ruby's dad.

14:20.027 --> 14:21.261
[Sarah on phone]
<i>Mr. Roth.</i>

14:21.696 --> 14:23.897
- <i>What's going on?</i>
-Everything's fine.

14:24.031 --> 14:26.066
<i>The Police called my mum</i>
<i>looking for Ruby.</i>

14:26.300 --> 14:28.135
-Sarah, listen.
- <i>What, what did you do?</i>

14:28.268 --> 14:30.204
-Sarah, listen to me.
- <i>I don't, don't think I should.</i>

14:30.337 --> 14:31.972
-Sarah!
- <i>You're scaring me!</i>

14:32.139 --> 14:33.842
[Sarah] <i>I'm not supposed</i>
<i>to be talking to you.</i>

14:34.408 --> 14:36.511
<i>How did you even get my number?</i>

14:37.411 --> 14:40.582
You texted me today
to meet you at school.

14:40.715 --> 14:42.316
[Sarah] <i>You texted me!</i>

14:42.684 --> 14:44.351
Sarah, I didn't meet you
until this afternoon.

14:44.485 --> 14:46.120
How would I have your number?

14:46.387 --> 14:47.856
[Sarah] <i>I should hang up.</i>

14:47.988 --> 14:49.356
No, no, no, Sarah,
I need your help.

14:49.490 --> 14:51.291
Okay, you were the last person

14:51.425 --> 14:53.160
to talk to Ruby last night.

14:53.595 --> 14:56.765
[sobs] <i>Not like in person.</i>
<i>We Snapchatted.</i>

14:57.565 --> 15:00.467
-What exactly did she say?
- <i>I told you already.</i>

15:00.968 --> 15:02.469
[Tom]
Tell me again.

15:02.637 --> 15:04.104
[Sarah] <i>She said she was</i>
<i>looking for her father,</i>

15:04.238 --> 15:05.807
<i>but he wasn't answering.</i>

15:06.140 --> 15:09.143
Yeah I was out late.
I was, it was really late,

15:09.276 --> 15:11.211
and I didn't hear her message
until this morning.

15:11.546 --> 15:13.748
[Sarah] <i>Could've meant her other</i>
<i>father. She just said father!</i>

15:13.882 --> 15:17.117
<i>I don't know which one.</i>
<i>Then she sent me the picture.</i>

15:17.418 --> 15:19.086
<i>I took a screenshot.</i>

15:19.219 --> 15:20.954
Okay, what happened
to the original?

15:21.121 --> 15:23.725
-[Sarah] <i>It-it-it disappeared.</i>
-What?

15:23.957 --> 15:26.026
[Sarah] <i>You know... Snapchat?</i>

15:27.060 --> 15:29.129
Yes. Sarah,
have you told your mum

15:29.263 --> 15:31.633
or the police
about the photograph, about--

15:31.766 --> 15:34.301
[Sarah] <i>God no! Ruby made me</i>
<i>swear never to tell anyone!</i>

15:34.869 --> 15:37.505
<i>And I deleted the picture</i>
<i>like you said.</i>

15:39.006 --> 15:42.309
Sarah, there's a reason
that you confided in me today.

15:42.443 --> 15:45.145
Why you showed me the photo
and no one else.

15:45.446 --> 15:47.381
[Sarah] <i>Because, like,</i>
<i>you're her dad.</i>

15:47.515 --> 15:49.784
That's right. I'm her dad.
I'm her dad, Sarah.

15:49.918 --> 15:51.151
Now I need your help.

15:51.285 --> 15:54.254
Is there anyone or anywhere

15:54.388 --> 15:56.390
you can think of
that she might be?

15:56.624 --> 15:58.325
[Sarah] <i>I don't want him</i>
<i>to get in trouble.</i>

15:58.459 --> 15:59.894
<i>No one's getting in trouble,</i>
<i>Sarah.</i>

16:00.127 --> 16:02.029
<i>She could be with Dario.</i>

16:02.664 --> 16:03.964
Who the fuck is Dario?

16:04.231 --> 16:06.568
-[Sarah] <i>Her boyfriend.</i>
-Boyfriend? She's 12.

16:06.734 --> 16:09.403
-[Sarah] <i>He's older.</i>
-Jesus fucking Christ.

16:09.537 --> 16:11.573
[Sarah] <i>He's in grade seven!</i>

16:13.641 --> 16:15.375
Okay, give me Dario's number.

16:15.677 --> 16:17.712
[Sarah] <i>I... I don't know</i>
<i>if I should.</i>

16:17.879 --> 16:20.047
<i>I'm supposed to</i>
<i>contact the police if...</i>

16:20.214 --> 16:21.850
Give me Dario's number, Sarah.

16:21.982 --> 16:24.251
And then you can call the police
and you can tell them we talked.

16:24.384 --> 16:27.387
All I care about is Ruby
and finding her.

16:29.990 --> 16:32.192
I'm worried about her, Sarah.

16:33.227 --> 16:34.929
Ruby's impulsive, you know.

16:35.395 --> 16:38.900
Like... Like that time, she-she
spray-painted the teacher's car

16:39.399 --> 16:40.668
[Sarah] <i>What?</i>

16:41.068 --> 16:43.605
When he told her she should
smile more. Remember?

16:44.338 --> 16:46.473
[Sarah] <i>That might have been</i>
<i>her old school.</i>

16:47.509 --> 16:49.309
I'm worried she's going
to do something to herself.

16:49.443 --> 16:51.345
That she, that she,
might hurt herself.

16:53.046 --> 16:56.316
[Sarah] <i>Okay.</i>
<i>I texted you Dario's number.</i>

16:57.284 --> 16:58.887
Yeah, thank you.
Thank you, Sarah.

16:59.052 --> 17:01.154
[Sarah] <i>Look she...</i>
