<i>-Incoming call...</i>
-Answer.

43:44.492 --> 43:45.693
<i>Make it go away.</i>

43:45.826 --> 43:46.861
<i>I'm begging you.</i>

43:46.994 --> 43:48.262
Ruby, what's happening?

43:48.395 --> 43:50.431
<i>Make it go away. Please.</i>

43:50.565 --> 43:53.334
-Ruby!
<i>-Make it go away!</i>

43:57.838 --> 43:59.306
[The Associate]
<i>Relax, Tom.</i>

44:00.007 --> 44:01.610
<i>They're gone.</i>

44:01.742 --> 44:03.210
<i>Congratulations.</i>

44:03.344 --> 44:06.280
<i>You convinced them you're a man</i>
<i>to be taken seriously,</i>

44:06.413 --> 44:07.781
<i>to be feared.</i>

44:08.249 --> 44:09.917
[sobbing]
You convinced them.

44:10.050 --> 44:12.353
You put those words
in my daughter's mouth.

44:12.486 --> 44:15.990
<i>The point is,</i>
<i>the message came from you, Tom.</i>

44:16.123 --> 44:18.959
<i>It's the message you wanted</i>
<i>to send.</i>

44:26.200 --> 44:28.202
[Ruby]
<i>Make it go away!</i>

44:28.702 --> 44:29.904
<i>I'm begging you.</i>

44:30.037 --> 44:31.372
<i>Make it go away!</i>

44:31.506 --> 44:32.773
<i>Please.</i>

44:32.907 --> 44:34.942
<i>Make it go away!</i>

44:37.444 --> 44:39.213
[sobbing]

44:41.982 --> 44:44.018
You sent this from my phone.

44:45.886 --> 44:47.321
Who are you?

44:48.489 --> 44:50.824
Is this a game to you?
Are you even human?

44:50.958 --> 44:52.793
[The Associate] <i>We have</i>
<i>45 minutes left</i>

44:52.927 --> 44:54.762
<i>in our session, Tom.</i>

44:54.895 --> 44:56.864
<i>You may spend it however</i>
<i>you wish,</i>

44:56.997 --> 44:58.699
<i>but I should remind you</i>

44:58.832 --> 45:01.268
<i>this is a life or death</i>
<i>situation.</i>

45:02.036 --> 45:06.774
<i>I'd prefer it if we focused</i>
<i>our conversation on you, Tom.</i>

45:07.308 --> 45:09.476
<i>Let's talk about you, shall we?</i>

45:09.611 --> 45:11.312
[sobbing]

45:12.079 --> 45:13.914
Will it help me get
my daughter back?

45:14.048 --> 45:16.551
<i>I'm afraid it's the only way.</i>

45:17.218 --> 45:19.887
<i>We can talk while you drive.</i>

45:20.655 --> 45:23.791
<i>Continue east on this road.</i>

45:23.924 --> 45:25.926
<i>Take the first left.</i>

45:27.361 --> 45:29.997
<i>What would you like</i>
<i>to talk about, Tom?</i>

45:30.565 --> 45:33.000
What do you want
in exchange for Ruby?

45:34.235 --> 45:36.705
<i>You're very fond of her,</i>
<i>aren't you?</i>

45:37.238 --> 45:39.340
She's my daughter, isn't she?

45:39.473 --> 45:40.575
<i>You love her.</i>

45:40.709 --> 45:42.176
Of course I fucking love her.

45:42.309 --> 45:45.412
<i>This love you have</i>
<i>for your daughter.</i>

45:45.547 --> 45:47.414
<i>Is it reciprocated?</i>

45:47.549 --> 45:50.117
Daughters love their dads
when they're little.

45:50.251 --> 45:51.852
<i>And now?</i>

45:57.324 --> 46:00.261
<i>I see by your employment</i>
<i>history, Tom,</i>

46:00.394 --> 46:03.864
<i>a high turnover of jobs</i>
<i>in a curious variety</i>

46:03.998 --> 46:05.899
<i>of unrelated fields.</i>

46:06.033 --> 46:07.968
What can I say.
I get bored easy.

46:08.102 --> 46:10.971
<i>But it appears this pattern</i>
<i>of impulsiveness</i>

46:11.105 --> 46:14.208
<i>extends to all aspects</i>
<i>of your life.</i>

46:16.143 --> 46:18.546
<i>You might be interested to know</i>
<i>that you suffer</i>

46:18.680 --> 46:23.117
<i>an undiagnosed attention</i>
<i>deficit hyperactivity disorder.</i>

46:23.851 --> 46:25.886
<i>You have a condition, Tom.</i>

46:26.020 --> 46:28.590
Great. I wish I'd known.

46:28.723 --> 46:30.958
<i>It wouldn't have</i>
<i>made any difference.</i>

46:31.091 --> 46:32.893
<i>You are who you are, Tom.</i>

46:33.027 --> 46:35.697
<i>Life is just a series</i>
<i>of choices.</i>

46:35.829 --> 46:38.198
<i>Right, wrong, good, bad,</i>

46:38.332 --> 46:40.934
<i>actions and consequences.</i>

46:41.068 --> 46:42.403
<i>It's really very simple.</i>

46:42.537 --> 46:44.805
I don't want to talk about me
anymore.

46:46.775 --> 46:48.942
<i>Let's talk about Ruby.</i>

46:53.013 --> 46:55.382
[intense music]

47:19.873 --> 47:21.509
<i>Easy, Tom.</i>

47:21.643 --> 47:24.546
<i>You don't have any points</i>
<i>left on your license.</i>

47:33.354 --> 47:36.957
<i>It's best to accept</i>
<i>the inevitable, Tom.</i>

47:37.091 --> 47:39.259
<i>It's not a matter</i>
<i>of my patience.</i>

47:39.393 --> 47:43.364
<i>I'm enjoying our discussion</i>
<i>and getting to know you.</i>

47:43.964 --> 47:46.735
<i>It's just that</i>
<i>we have so little time.</i>

47:46.867 --> 47:48.636
<i>And this is, if you recall...</i>

47:48.770 --> 47:50.337
A matter of life and death.

47:50.471 --> 47:53.874
<i>Yes. I think we should</i>
<i>get to the point, Tom.</i>

47:54.007 --> 47:55.376
Please.

47:55.510 --> 47:58.278
<i>There's a reason</i>
<i>I was called in.</i>

47:58.780 --> 48:00.849
<i>There's always a reason.</i>

48:01.348 --> 48:03.283
I just want my daughter back.

48:03.417 --> 48:07.187
<i>Once you've compensated</i>
<i>for the loss, it's only fair.</i>

48:07.722 --> 48:10.190
<i>Someone has to pay</i>
<i>for Shane Bader.</i>

48:10.324 --> 48:11.793
He got what he deserved.

48:11.925 --> 48:14.562
<i>But you interrupted</i>
<i>a negotiation, Tom.</i>

48:14.696 --> 48:17.732
<i>He and I were in the middle</i>
<i>of a pleasant conversation.</i>

48:17.866 --> 48:20.501
<i>Much like the one</i>
<i>you and I are having,</i>

48:20.635 --> 48:22.871
<i>at this very moment.</i>

48:23.003 --> 48:25.472
<i>He, too, was in a life or death</i>
<i>situation,</i>

48:25.607 --> 48:28.942
<i>the nature of which</i>
<i>I'm not at liberty to reveal.</i>

48:29.476 --> 48:33.914
<i>Trust me. These mistakes</i>
<i>happen all the time, Tom.</i>

48:34.047 --> 48:35.382
<i>You're only human.</i>

48:36.316 --> 48:40.220
<i>But the fact remains, Mr. Bader</i>
<i>wasn't yours to judge.</i>

48:40.354 --> 48:41.856
You don't know what he did.

48:41.989 --> 48:44.324
<i>You'd be surprised what I know.</i>

48:44.458 --> 48:46.694
Any father would have done
the same.

48:48.696 --> 48:50.164
She's my daughter.

48:52.834 --> 48:54.234
I'm sorry.

48:54.736 --> 48:56.604
<i>Sorry for what, Tom?</i>

48:57.271 --> 48:58.706
<i>Your temper?</i>

48:59.607 --> 49:00.842
Can you blame me?

49:00.974 --> 49:02.911
<i>You are who you are, Tom.</i>

49:03.043 --> 49:07.147
<i>The apportion of blame</i>
<i>is relevant only to actions.</i>

49:07.649 --> 49:09.684
<i>But looking back</i>
<i>over your history</i>

49:09.818 --> 49:13.487
<i>and the events leading</i>
<i>to our discussion today,</i>

49:13.621 --> 49:17.224
<i>I'm afraid your temper</i>
<i>must be viewed as causation.</i>

49:17.357 --> 49:20.695
My temper wasn't the problem.
It was the drink that did me in.

49:21.962 --> 49:23.665
But I've been sober for years.

49:23.798 --> 49:28.368
<i>Eight years, seven months,</i>
<i>13 days to be exact.</i>

49:29.938 --> 49:33.508
This is the day my wife left me,
and took away my little girl.

49:34.676 --> 49:37.512
<i>She left you because of your</i>
<i>drinking.</i>

49:38.045 --> 49:39.781
When I drank I got mean.

49:40.682 --> 49:45.052
<i>And your sobriety hasn't really</i>
<i>resolved your anger issues?</i>

49:45.587 --> 49:47.488
<i>-Has it?</i>
-Not really.

49:48.455 --> 49:51.091
<i>-You're still angry?</i>
-Of course I'm fucking angry.

49:51.726 --> 49:54.328
I lost my only daughter,
I've lost my kid!

49:54.461 --> 49:56.296
<i>And you blame Shane Bader.</i>

49:56.430 --> 49:58.098
Well, he kept her from me,
didn't he?

49:58.232 --> 50:01.201
<i>His actions fall well</i>
<i>within his rights, Tom.</i>

50:01.335 --> 50:04.137
<i>He was after all her legal</i>
<i>custodian.</i>

50:04.271 --> 50:05.773
Not anymore!

50:08.242 --> 50:10.444
I saved her from that sick fuck.

50:10.578 --> 50:13.581
<i>Have you, Tom,</i>
<i>saved your daughter?</i>

50:13.715 --> 50:16.416
Yeah, mate, I did. I saved her
from the unspeakable.

50:16.551 --> 50:19.119
<i>About that photograph, Tom.</i>

50:19.654 --> 50:23.825
<i>No doubt you've considered</i>
<i>the power of that single image.</i>

50:24.592 --> 50:27.929
<i>The havoc it could wreak</i>
<i>on your daughter's innocence.</i>

50:28.763 --> 50:32.165
<i>What if there is</i>
<i>more than one image, Tom?</i>

50:33.433 --> 50:37.070
<i>What if Mr. Bader kept videos?</i>

50:41.910 --> 50:44.278
<i>Anything is possible.</i>

50:49.116 --> 50:51.819
<i>You need to be certain, Tom.</i>

50:58.793 --> 51:00.662
Tell me what to do.

51:04.164 --> 51:08.101
<i>Are you familiar</i>
<i>with Shane Bader's office?</i>

51:10.270 --> 51:12.339
It's above his garage.

51:12.472 --> 51:14.642
<i>You need to burn it, Tom.</i>

51:14.776 --> 51:17.879
-Burn down his office?
<i>-The entire garage.</i>

51:18.012 --> 51:20.247
<i>You need to burn it</i>
<i>to the ground.</i>

51:20.380 --> 51:22.050
Like now? It's impossible.

51:22.182 --> 51:25.787
<i>I'll need proof, of course.</i>
<i>A video text is fine.</i>

51:25.920 --> 51:27.722
I can't go back there.
They're waiting for me.

51:27.855 --> 51:30.892
<i>It's the only way to save</i>
<i>your daughter, Tom.</i>

51:31.025 --> 51:32.860
<i>There are still 37 minutes.</i>

51:32.994 --> 51:35.495
What happens if I don't make it?
What happens to Ruby?

51:36.430 --> 51:37.732
<i>Ruby dies.</i>

51:38.198 --> 51:39.701
[screaming]

51:42.637 --> 51:44.739
Fuck! Fuck!

51:45.238 --> 51:46.641
Fuck.

51:47.709 --> 51:49.711
[sobbing]

51:58.086 --> 52:01.154
[intense music]

52:22.275 --> 52:24.211
[grunts]

52:33.788 --> 52:35.590
[grunting]

52:43.698 --> 52:45.967
[The Associate]
<i>You're wasting valuable time.</i>

52:46.567 --> 52:48.703
<i>You need to burn the garage.</i>

52:48.836 --> 52:50.772
<i>You need to burn it</i>
<i>to the ground.</i>

52:50.905 --> 52:52.172
Fuck!

52:54.108 --> 52:55.677
What the fuck?

53:01.248 --> 53:02.550
Fuck

53:03.417 --> 53:05.820
Mate, come on!

53:06.353 --> 53:08.022
Work!

53:08.156 --> 53:09.624
Fuck!

53:20.935 --> 53:22.235
Call Terri.

53:22.369 --> 53:23.805
[automated voice]
<i>Calling Terri.</i>

53:24.337 --> 53:25.773
<i>-Tom.</i>
-Where are you?

53:25.907 --> 53:27.909
<i>I'm at my house, Tom.</i>
<i>Where are you?</i>

53:28.042 --> 53:29.476
<i>The cops aren't fucking around</i>
<i>anymore.</i>

53:29.610 --> 53:31.045
<i>I can't keep lying to them.</i>

53:31.179 --> 53:32.747
<i>Put your camera on.</i>
<i>I want to talk to Ruby.</i>

53:32.880 --> 53:34.214
I told you I'm bringing her
home, okay?

53:34.347 --> 53:35.516
I gave you my word.

53:35.650 --> 53:36.918
<i>Oh, your word means shit to me,</i>
<i>Tom.</i>

53:37.051 --> 53:37.952
Are you near anyone right now?

53:38.086 --> 53:39.153
Can anyone hear you?

53:39.286 --> 53:40.320
<i>I'm on the street, Tom.</i>

53:40.454 --> 53:41.656
<i>I'm not a fucking idiot!</i>

53:41.789 --> 53:43.323
Terri, it's worse than you
think.

53:43.457 --> 53:44.692
<i>What is?</i>

53:44.826 --> 53:46.393
The shit your pedophile husband
was into.

53:46.527 --> 53:48.196
The people he's dealing with
is bad.

53:48.328 --> 53:49.630
<i>You're scaring me, Tom.</i>

53:49.764 --> 53:52.399
I don't have her, Terri.
She's not with me.

53:55.469 --> 53:57.237
Someone's holding her
for ransom.

53:57.370 --> 53:58.940
<i>Ransom?</i>

53:59.073 --> 54:03.578
Someone who's in business
with your husband or was.

54:03.711 --> 54:06.114
<i>-We need to tell the cops.</i>
-No! No cops.

54:06.246 --> 54:09.016
Okay? That's his rule.
No one knows besides you and me.

54:10.484 --> 54:12.019
And Ruby's boyfriend.

54:12.153 --> 54:13.755
<i>Boyfriend?</i>

54:13.888 --> 54:16.057
<i>What boyfriend?</i>
<i>Ruby doesn't have a boyfriend.</i>

54:16.190 --> 54:17.792
-Dario.
<i>-Dario?</i>

54:17.925 --> 54:19.660
<i>The nerdy kid</i>
<i>from down the street?</i>

54:19.794 --> 54:21.028
<i>Dario.</i>

54:21.162 --> 54:22.997
<i>You spoke to Dario.</i>
<i>Oh, my God, Tom.</i>

54:23.131 --> 54:24.932
<i>You're a curse.</i>
<i>You're a fucking...</i>

54:25.066 --> 54:26.934
-I'm trying to make up for it
<i>-...curse, that's what you are.</i>

54:27.068 --> 54:28.736
-But I'm running out of time.
-Curse that will never go away.

54:28.870 --> 54:30.403
Ask Dario, he'll tell you.

54:30.538 --> 54:32.272
<i>Can you put your camera on?</i>

54:32.405 --> 54:34.242
<i>I need to see your face.</i>
<i>I've never trusted your voice.</i>

54:34.374 --> 54:35.877
There's more than one photo.

54:37.377 --> 54:39.046
Maybe even video. Who knows.

54:41.849 --> 54:44.652
<i>Oh, my God. Our little girl.</i>

54:45.520 --> 54:48.556
<i>That's what this is about?</i>
<i>They're blackmailing us?</i>

54:48.689 --> 54:50.625
<i>Oh! What do they want, Tom?</i>

54:50.758 --> 54:52.593
They ordered me to burn down
your husband's office.

54:52.727 --> 54:54.228
The whole fucking garage.

54:54.361 --> 54:55.797
They told me to burn it
all down or else...

54:56.496 --> 54:58.365
<i>Or else what?</i>

55:01.334 --> 55:02.637
<i>Tom!</i>

55:02.770 --> 55:04.071
Look, we only have 30 minutes,
okay?

55:04.205 --> 55:05.472
We have no choice.

55:05.606 --> 55:07.108
You have to burn down
the garage.

55:07.241 --> 55:08.276
<i>-Me?</i>
-Yes.

55:08.408 --> 55:09.644
<i>Why me?</i>

55:09.777 --> 55:11.378
-I'm too far away.
-I can't.

55:11.512 --> 55:12.580
I don't know where I am,
I'll never get there.

55:12.713 --> 55:14.381
<i>There's cops everywhere.</i>

55:14.515 --> 55:15.983
-It's a fucking crime scene...
-You have to do it, Terri.

55:16.117 --> 55:17.919
You have to burn down
the garage.

55:18.052 --> 55:19.620
You have to video it and
you have to text me the video.

55:19.754 --> 55:21.589
- <i>Why? What's in the garage?</i>
-Photos.

55:21.722 --> 55:23.858
Everything! The proof of what
he did to our little girl.

55:25.960 --> 55:27.695
[Terri sobbing]

55:29.530 --> 55:33.634
<i>Um, he keeps</i>
<i>two jerrycans of petrol</i>

55:33.768 --> 55:36.336
<i>in the garage</i>
<i>for the generator.</i>

55:36.469 --> 55:38.338
Yeah, yeah, yeah, that's it.
Use them, use them.

55:38.471 --> 55:40.141
I know you can do this.

55:40.942 --> 55:43.711
<i>I'll do it. I'll burn it down.</i>
<i>I'll burn it.</i>

55:43.845 --> 55:45.813
-I love you, Terri.
<i>-Fuck you, Tom.</i>

55:45.947 --> 55:48.015
<i>-I'm doing this for Ruby.</i>
-Well, send proof. Text...

55:48.149 --> 55:49.650
[cell phone beeps]

55:54.622 --> 55:56.190
[cell phone ringing]

55:56.324 --> 55:59.227
[automated voice] <i>Incoming call</i>
<i>from Emergency Services.</i>

55:59.359 --> 56:01.028
Answer.

56:01.162 --> 56:02.930
[Abigail] <i>I can't hold the</i>
<i>police back much longer.</i>

56:03.064 --> 56:05.233
The cops don't know where I am
or where I'm going

56:05.365 --> 56:06.366
and neither do I.

56:06.499 --> 56:07.568
That's the whole point.

56:07.702 --> 56:08.903
That's the reason I need time.

56:09.036 --> 56:10.771
[Abigail]
<i>What's the reason, Tom?</i>

56:11.038 --> 56:12.340
To save Ruby.

56:12.573 --> 56:14.407
[Abigail] <i>Is that</i>
<i>what this is all about?</i>

56:14.575 --> 56:15.910
<i>Saving Ruby?</i>

56:16.043 --> 56:17.044
29 minutes.

56:17.178 --> 56:18.512
I just need 29 minutes,

56:18.646 --> 56:20.848
and God as my witness,
I'm bringing Ruby home.

56:20.982 --> 56:22.817
[Abigail]
<i>What happens in 29 Minutes?</i>

56:22.950 --> 56:24.218
It's all over.

56:24.484 --> 56:25.653
He'll love this, it's over.

56:25.786 --> 56:27.088
<i>Tom, we need to know that you</i>

56:27.221 --> 56:28.322
<i>haven't harmed</i>
<i>your daught...</i>

56:28.455 --> 56:29.891
[phone disconnected]

56:35.196 --> 56:37.531
[The Associate]
<i>It's out of your hands, Tom.</i>

56:37.765 --> 56:39.200
No, no, no.
I've sorted out the fire.

56:39.333 --> 56:41.302
I'm going to text you the video
as soon as I get it.

56:41.434 --> 56:42.670
You have my word.

56:42.970 --> 56:44.739
[The Associate]
<i>We need to talk. Tom.</i>

56:45.239 --> 56:48.376
<i>Why don't you continue</i>
<i>straight along this route</i>

56:48.809 --> 56:50.845
<i>to the next traffic light.</i>

56:52.013 --> 56:54.447
[engine revving]

57:01.055 --> 57:02.723
[The Associate]
<i>At the traffic light,</i>

57:03.024 --> 57:06.493
<i>there's an establishment</i>
<i>on the far corner.</i>

57:06.694 --> 57:08.262
<i>You're going to park</i>

57:08.596 --> 57:10.031
<i>and enter it.</i>

57:13.968 --> 57:16.804
[dramatic music]

57:23.711 --> 57:26.847
[The Associate]
<i>Go and see the takeout man.</i>

57:33.486 --> 57:34.855
I've been here before.

57:35.089 --> 57:36.424
[The Associate]
<i>There's something you need</i>

57:36.557 --> 57:38.192
<i>to pick up, Tom.</i>

57:38.826 --> 57:40.728
[The Associate]
<i>Bring your phone with you.</i>

57:44.799 --> 57:46.801
<i>And your ear phones.</i>

57:47.335 --> 57:49.469
<i>That way we can talk.</i>

57:55.343 --> 57:58.579
<i>Try the beverage cup</i>
<i>in the drink holder.</i>

58:07.421 --> 58:09.991
[crickets chirping]

58:10.157 --> 58:11.759
[dogs barking]

58:13.260 --> 58:16.030
[suspenseful music]

58:26.374 --> 58:28.142
[The Associate]
<i>Ring the buzzer, Tom.</i>

58:30.578 --> 58:32.046
[buzzer ringing]

58:39.387 --> 58:40.621
What next?

58:41.022 --> 58:42.823
[The Associate]
<i>We need to talk about Terri.</i>

58:43.124 --> 58:46.894
<i>About you bringing her</i>
<i>into your situation.</i>

58:48.496 --> 58:49.964
I had no choice.

58:56.837 --> 58:58.305
Can I help you?

59:00.441 --> 59:01.942
[whispering] Am I supposed
to ask him for something?

59:02.076 --> 59:03.811
-What's that?
-I'm not talking to you.

59:04.211 --> 59:06.580
[The Associate] <i>He knows</i>
<i>what to give you, Tom.</i>

59:07.548 --> 59:09.016
<i>They all do.</i>

59:11.685 --> 59:13.120
I remember you.

59:15.456 --> 59:16.724
You know what I want?

59:17.024 --> 59:18.793
It's been a long time.

59:19.994 --> 59:22.897
-I can't remember.
-You know what I want?

59:27.001 --> 59:28.869
[The Associate] <i>You've been</i>
<i>in this place before,</i>

59:29.003 --> 59:30.104
<i>haven't you?</i>

59:30.505 --> 59:32.339
I've been to a lot of
bottle shops, mate.

59:32.541 --> 59:34.509
[The Associate] <i>I thought</i>
<i>this might be a good place</i>

59:34.642 --> 59:36.343
<i>to discuss your ex wife.</i>

59:36.477 --> 59:38.879
You can rely on Terri,
she's tougher than you think.

59:39.080 --> 59:40.414
[The Associate] <i>Glancing</i>
<i>through her history,</i>

59:40.549 --> 59:42.850
<i>I'd have to agree with you.</i>

59:44.785 --> 59:46.620
We've done a lot of hateful shit
to each other,

59:46.754 --> 59:48.589
but deep down,
there's a lot of respect.

59:48.756 --> 59:52.660
[The Associate] <i>Tell me about</i>
<i>the incident at the motel, Tom</i>

59:52.793 --> 59:54.128
<i>concerning Ruby.</i>

59:54.328 --> 59:55.996
It wasn't an incident.
It was an accident.

59:56.263 --> 59:58.099
[The Associate]
<i>Tell me about it.</i>

59:58.265 --> 59:59.333
Let it go.

59:59.467 --> 01:00:01.135
[car window opening]

01:00:03.104 --> 01:00:05.005
[sighing]

01:00:06.674 --> 01:00:08.109
She was three.

01:00:08.510 --> 01:00:09.743
It was a fluke accident.

01:00:09.877 --> 01:00:11.278
She wasn't hurt.

01:00:11.546 --> 01:00:14.516
[The Associate]
<i>I'm not sure Ruby would agree.</i>

01:00:14.748 --> 01:00:16.217
Did I hurt her?

01:00:16.450 --> 01:00:17.685
Was anything broken?

01:00:17.918 --> 01:00:19.153
[The Associate]
<i>Only her heart.</i>

01:00:19.386 --> 01:00:20.589
That's on her mother.

01:00:21.222 --> 01:00:23.924
She fucking poisoned
her memory of me.

01:00:24.191 --> 01:00:26.260
She made me
into something I'm not.

01:00:27.161 --> 01:00:29.396
I am not that guy anymore.

01:00:30.264 --> 01:00:33.634
Ruby's going to see
that I'm not that guy anymore!

01:00:34.268 --> 01:00:35.936
[bottle smashing]

01:00:37.471 --> 01:00:40.741
[The Associate]
<i>I have some unfortunate news.</i>

01:00:40.975 --> 01:00:43.110
<i>Your plan isn't going to work.</i>

01:00:43.244 --> 01:00:45.614
<i>You're going to fail</i>
<i>at your task.</i>

01:00:46.080 --> 01:00:47.815
<i>I'm only telling you this</i>

01:00:47.982 --> 01:00:49.950
<i>because there's so little time.</i>

01:00:50.117 --> 01:00:52.720
-Terri is going to come through.
<i>-It's a crime scene, Tom.</i>

01:00:52.887 --> 01:00:55.756
[The Associate] <i>The suspect's</i>
<i>whereabouts are unknown.</i>

01:00:55.890 --> 01:00:57.958
<i>The police are prepared</i>
<i>and alert.</i>

01:00:58.092 --> 01:01:00.661
<i>These are highly skilled</i>
<i>professionals.</i>

01:01:00.794 --> 01:01:02.696
Anything is possible.
No one knows the future.

01:01:02.830 --> 01:01:05.166
[The Associate]
<i>I'm an expert in probabilities.</i>

01:01:05.299 --> 01:01:07.501
<i>The odds aren't</i>
<i>in Terri's favor.</i>

01:01:07.636 --> 01:01:09.069
How do you know?

01:01:09.937 --> 01:01:11.138
[The Associate]
<i>I've been called in</i>

01:01:11.338 --> 01:01:13.674
<i>to mediate</i>
<i>Terri's situation. Tom.</i>

01:01:13.807 --> 01:01:15.109
What happens to Terri?

01:01:15.644 --> 01:01:17.646
[The Associate] <i>It's out of</i>
<i>your hands now, Tom.</i>

01:01:17.778 --> 01:01:20.681
[intense music]

01:01:22.750 --> 01:01:24.852
[inhales sharply]

01:01:38.365 --> 01:01:39.800
What about Ruby?

01:01:43.370 --> 01:01:45.372
that failed you, not me.

01:01:46.340 --> 01:01:49.009
Yeah, I made her do it,
but I didn't have a choice.

01:01:49.877 --> 01:01:52.146
Please don't take Ruby from me.

01:01:54.915 --> 01:01:56.917
Look I did my best!

01:01:58.052 --> 01:02:00.921
I tried, trying counts
for something.

01:02:04.458 --> 01:02:05.459
I made the mistake.

01:02:05.594 --> 01:02:06.994
Don't punish Ruby for it.

01:02:07.127 --> 01:02:08.362
Please.

01:02:09.964 --> 01:02:12.399
I promised I'd bring her home.

01:02:15.903 --> 01:02:17.071
I'm begging you!

01:02:17.204 --> 01:02:19.840
Give me one more chance
to save her.

01:02:20.474 --> 01:02:22.443
[The Associate]
<i>There's so little time, Tom.</i>

01:02:22.977 --> 01:02:26.213
There's 18 minutes.
I will do anything.

01:02:27.348 --> 01:02:29.183
[The Associate]
<i>If you insist</i>

01:02:29.316 --> 01:02:33.153
<i>when the light changes continue</i>
<i>straight, no matter what.</i>

01:02:33.287 --> 01:02:35.523
<i>No turns, no detours.</i>

01:02:35.657 --> 01:02:37.525
<i>Head straight along the road.</i>

01:02:37.692 --> 01:02:39.360
<i>-Is that clear?</i>
-Yes.

01:02:39.561 --> 01:02:42.796
<i>-It's the most direct route.</i>
-Back to Ruby?

01:02:42.930 --> 01:02:44.798
[The Associate]
<i>It's the only way.</i>

01:02:45.332 --> 01:02:47.334
<i>I'll need your word on this.</i>

01:02:47.501 --> 01:02:49.704
I'm heading straight.
God is my witness.

01:02:49.870 --> 01:02:52.840
[The Associate] <i>You're not</i>
<i>negotiating in good faith, Tom.</i>

01:02:52.973 --> 01:02:55.142
<i>I happen to know</i>
<i>you're an atheist.</i>

01:02:55.276 --> 01:02:57.444
<i>I need a valid pledge.</i>

01:02:58.279 --> 01:03:01.115
<i>I'll need you to swear</i>
<i>on your daughter's life.</i>

01:03:01.482 --> 01:03:03.450
[sobbing]

01:03:05.419 --> 01:03:09.123
I-I swear on Ruby's life,
I'm heading straight.

01:03:09.691 --> 01:03:11.025
[The Associate] <i>There's</i>
<i>something you need</i>

01:03:11.158 --> 01:03:12.860
<i>to pick up, Tom.</i>

01:03:15.029 --> 01:03:17.064
[inhaling sharply]

01:03:19.066 --> 01:03:22.303
[intense music]

01:03:34.783 --> 01:03:37.284
[neck cracking]

01:03:45.059 --> 01:03:47.895
[intense music]

01:03:54.602 --> 01:03:55.836
[telephone ringing]

01:03:56.403 --> 01:03:57.838
[automated voice] <i>Incoming</i>
<i>call from Dario Khalid.</i>

01:03:57.971 --> 01:03:59.541
Answer.

01:04:00.040 --> 01:04:01.509
[Dario] <i>Mr. Roth?</i>

01:04:02.510 --> 01:04:03.977
<i>It's Dario.</i>

01:04:06.447 --> 01:04:09.283
<i>I know because of your, uh,</i>
<i>situation or whatever,</i>

01:04:09.416 --> 01:04:12.252
<i>you don't know your daughter</i>
<i>very well, or like at all.</i>

01:04:12.419 --> 01:04:14.488
<i>But Ruby takes off</i>
<i>all the time.</i>

01:04:14.622 --> 01:04:17.157
<i>To be alone, or chill,</i>
<i>whatever, that sort of thing.</i>

01:04:17.291 --> 01:04:19.426
<i>And like I've tracked her</i>
<i>phone before.</i>

01:04:19.561 --> 01:04:21.095
<i>I've been at it</i>
<i>ever since I spoke to you.</i>

01:04:21.228 --> 01:04:23.163
You've tracked my
daughter's phone?

01:04:23.931 --> 01:04:25.834
[Dario] <i>Yeah.</i>
<i>Find my friends.</i>

01:04:26.133 --> 01:04:28.268
<i>I'm not picking up</i>
<i>any signal, Mr. Roth.</i>

01:04:28.402 --> 01:04:30.003
<i>They, they might have</i>
<i>removed the battery</i>

01:04:30.137 --> 01:04:31.706
<i>or put her phone</i>
<i>in a booster bag.</i>

01:04:31.840 --> 01:04:33.508
Nothing at all. That's it?

01:04:33.808 --> 01:04:36.410
[Dario] <i>I don't know anything</i>
<i>about hacking stuff, Mr. Roth.</i>

01:04:36.544 --> 01:04:38.780
<i>Find My Friends</i>
<i>wasn't just my best shot,</i>

01:04:38.946 --> 01:04:40.347
<i>it was my only shot.</i>

01:04:41.315 --> 01:04:42.717
And what about Ruby's message?

01:04:42.851 --> 01:04:44.251
[Dario sobbing]

01:04:44.586 --> 01:04:45.886
[Dario] <i>I heard a train horn</i>
<i>in the background</i>

01:04:46.019 --> 01:04:47.522
<i>but that could be anywhere.</i>

01:04:48.857 --> 01:04:50.592
<i>I'm really sorry, Mr. Roth.</i>

01:04:53.093 --> 01:04:54.895
You tried, mate.
Trying counts for something.

01:04:55.062 --> 01:04:56.463
[Dario]
<i>I really wanted to...</i>

01:04:56.897 --> 01:04:58.932
<i>I really wanted it to be me</i>
<i>that found her, Mr. Roth.</i>

01:04:59.066 --> 01:05:00.769
<i>To be the one that,</i>
<i>who saved her.</i>

01:05:00.901 --> 01:05:02.035
<i>Show her I was that guy.</i>

01:05:02.169 --> 01:05:03.370
<i>You know what I mean?</i>

01:05:03.505 --> 01:05:04.438
[Dario sobbing]

01:05:04.572 --> 01:05:05.640
I do, mate.

01:05:08.676 --> 01:05:09.811
I got to go now, Dario.

01:05:09.943 --> 01:05:12.279
[Dario] <i>I failed her, Mr. Roth.</i>

01:05:13.247 --> 01:05:15.784
-We all did.
<i>-Please save her.</i>

01:05:15.949 --> 01:05:17.351
[Dario] <i>You will, won't you?</i>

01:05:18.820 --> 01:05:20.254
God is my witness.

01:05:21.723 --> 01:05:23.157
[telephone disconnecting]

01:05:25.760 --> 01:05:27.194
[telephone ringing]

01:05:27.662 --> 01:05:29.631
[automated voice]
<i>Incoming call from work.</i>

01:05:29.764 --> 01:05:32.199
-Answer.
<i>-Tom, where the hell are ya?</i>

01:05:32.332 --> 01:05:33.701
[Trudy] <i>Benny's been</i>
<i>calling you.</i>

01:05:33.868 --> 01:05:35.870
<i>He got tired of waiting</i>
<i>and fucked off.</i>

01:05:36.403 --> 01:05:38.706
<i>You never fixed the leak</i>
<i>in the flare stack, Tom.</i>

01:05:38.873 --> 01:05:41.141
<i>Benny says you can</i>
<i>smell it from Mercy Road.</i>

01:05:41.275 --> 01:05:43.343
<i>This is a serious</i>
<i>liability issue</i>

01:05:43.578 --> 01:05:45.580
<i>I know you're new here,</i>
<i>but mate</i>

01:05:45.713 --> 01:05:48.883
<i>this is the third bloody time</i>
<i>you've stuffed up.</i>

01:05:49.016 --> 01:05:50.284
<i>Benny's sacking you, Tom.</i>

01:05:50.752 --> 01:05:52.620
<i>Sorry to be the one</i>
<i>to tell ya.</i>

01:05:53.253 --> 01:05:54.522
<i>We'll need the truck.</i>

01:05:54.656 --> 01:05:56.323
[dramatic music]

01:06:06.133 --> 01:06:07.201
Oh, thank Christ.

01:06:07.334 --> 01:06:08.969
I've seen you before.

01:06:09.236 --> 01:06:10.337
I passed you an hour ago.

01:06:10.471 --> 01:06:11.940
You weren't the only one, mate.

01:06:12.072 --> 01:06:13.373
It's been hell.

01:06:13.641 --> 01:06:14.909
You were on the other side
of the road there.

01:06:15.877 --> 01:06:17.745
That must have been
a hundred K's from here.

01:06:18.412 --> 01:06:19.514
Hey?

01:06:19.647 --> 01:06:20.981
What is this staged?

01:06:21.114 --> 01:06:22.550
What you on about?

01:06:23.250 --> 01:06:24.886
Are you one of his assistants?

01:06:25.018 --> 01:06:26.955
Listen, mate, I've got a flat,

01:06:27.087 --> 01:06:28.121
no spare,
no juice left in my phone.

01:06:28.255 --> 01:06:29.423
I've been out here forever,

01:06:29.624 --> 01:06:30.892
waving for help,
and nobody has stopped.

01:06:31.024 --> 01:06:32.560
Not one.

01:06:33.193 --> 01:06:34.829
People around here are cunts.

01:06:35.195 --> 01:06:36.598
I'm running out of time.
Give it to me.

01:06:36.865 --> 01:06:38.031
Hey?

01:06:38.332 --> 01:06:39.466
I'm supposed to pick
something up.

01:06:39.601 --> 01:06:40.935
What is it?

01:06:41.536 --> 01:06:43.303
Do you have anything for me?

01:06:44.071 --> 01:06:46.240
[dogs barking at distance]

01:06:47.675 --> 01:06:48.776
Head straight.

01:06:52.045 --> 01:06:54.281
Hey!
Hey, call someone.

01:06:54.414 --> 01:06:57.284
Tell them I'm stranded
on Mercy Road.

01:06:59.086 --> 01:07:00.220
You cunt!

01:07:00.487 --> 01:07:01.656
She's my daughter, Terri.

01:07:01.789 --> 01:07:03.625
God is my witness.

01:07:03.758 --> 01:07:06.528
[indistinct muttering]

01:07:10.899 --> 01:07:12.767
She's my daughter, Terri.
God is my witness.

01:07:12.901 --> 01:07:14.401
I'm bringing her home.

01:07:16.270 --> 01:07:19.139
[intense music]

01:07:23.076 --> 01:07:26.246
[car window opening]

01:07:28.348 --> 01:07:31.451
[Tom thinking] <i>Give her to me,</i>
<i>Terri, she's my daughter too.</i>

01:07:31.619 --> 01:07:34.154
-[Terri] <i>Stop, Tom, go away.</i>
-[Tom] <i>Give her to me, Terri.</i>

01:07:34.556 --> 01:07:35.990
-Terri give her to me.
-Oh, you're hurting her.

01:07:36.123 --> 01:07:39.192
[intense high-pitched shrill]

01:07:39.627 --> 01:07:41.596
[dogs barking]

01:07:48.036 --> 01:07:50.337
-[telephone ringing]
- <i>Incoming call from Terri.</i>

01:07:50.470 --> 01:07:52.105
Answer.
Terri! Thank God.

01:07:52.239 --> 01:07:54.107
[Abigail] <i>Tom, it's Abigail.</i>

01:07:54.408 --> 01:07:56.544
-Where's Terri?
<i>-There's been an accident.</i>

01:07:57.144 --> 01:07:59.914
[Abigail] <i>Two officers saw</i>
<i>somebody in Terri's garage--</i>

01:08:00.048 --> 01:08:01.549
Did the garage burn?

01:08:03.017 --> 01:08:04.519
[Abigail] <i>They assumed</i>
<i>it was you and--</i>

01:08:04.652 --> 01:08:06.888
Did the garage burn?
I need to know.

01:08:07.055 --> 01:08:08.322
[Abigail <i>Yes, Tom, it did.</i>

01:08:08.590 --> 01:08:10.725
I don't believe you,
send me proof.

01:08:10.858 --> 01:08:12.560
[telephone disconnected]

01:08:14.862 --> 01:08:17.096
I fucking did it.

01:08:19.600 --> 01:08:22.402
[The Associate] <i>Time to discuss</i>
<i>compensation, Tom.</i>

01:08:22.537 --> 01:08:24.072
No. Terri, Terri did it.

01:08:24.237 --> 01:08:25.640
I told you she'd come through.

01:08:25.872 --> 01:08:27.474
I didn't fail you.
I did exactly what you asked.

01:08:27.609 --> 01:08:29.077
We're even.
I swear they're going

01:08:29.209 --> 01:08:30.344
to send me proof any second now.

01:08:30.477 --> 01:08:31.478
[The Associate] <i>There's no need.</i>

01:08:31.613 --> 01:08:33.781
<i>I watched it live, Tom.</i>

01:08:33.982 --> 01:08:35.582
<i>Would you like to see?</i>

01:08:35.716 --> 01:08:37.051
[phone dinging]

01:08:37.585 --> 01:08:39.520
[Terri on recording] <i>Don't come</i>
<i>near me! Please stay away.</i>

01:08:39.654 --> 01:08:40.921
[gunshots]

01:08:41.055 --> 01:08:43.490
-[explosion]
-Terri!

01:08:44.993 --> 01:08:46.426
Terri!

01:08:46.861 --> 01:08:48.261
Terri!

01:08:50.130 --> 01:08:51.532
Terri.

01:08:53.968 --> 01:08:56.236
[sobbing]

01:09:01.509 --> 01:09:03.143
I did what you asked.

01:09:03.310 --> 01:09:05.379
[The Associate] <i>Consider your</i>
<i>debt for Mr. Bader</i>

01:09:05.513 --> 01:09:07.615
<i>paid in full, Tom.</i>

01:09:07.749 --> 01:09:11.719
<i>I'm afraid however,</i>
<i>you now owe for damages.</i>

01:09:12.352 --> 01:09:13.821
You're gonna make me
pay for Terri?

01:09:14.087 --> 01:09:16.890
[The Associate] <i>You brought her</i>
<i>into your situation, Tom.</i>

01:09:17.058 --> 01:09:18.091
<i>It's only fair.</i>

01:09:18.225 --> 01:09:20.962
No, not Ruby,
not my daughter.

01:09:21.161 --> 01:09:22.328
Don't hurt my daughter.

01:09:22.462 --> 01:09:23.997
Ruby, please.

01:09:24.765 --> 01:09:26.934
[The Associate]
<i>Someone always has to pay.</i>

01:09:27.167 --> 01:09:28.603
I'll pay!

01:09:29.269 --> 01:09:31.005
Let me be the one who pays.

01:09:31.438 --> 01:09:32.907
[The Associate]
<i>We made a deal, Tom.</i>

01:09:33.041 --> 01:09:34.274
I made a promise.

01:09:35.375 --> 01:09:39.379
[The Associate] <i>I'd like to</i>
<i>propose a new arrangement.</i>

01:09:46.821 --> 01:09:48.421
[The Associate]
<i>Go ahead, Tom.</i>

01:09:49.389 --> 01:09:50.825
<i>Open it.</i>

01:09:56.831 --> 01:10:00.267
-What's in there?
<i>-Don't be afraid, Tom.</i>

01:10:02.537 --> 01:10:04.438
[The Associate] <i>Reach inside.</i>

01:10:05.006 --> 01:10:06.607
<i>It won't bite.</i>

01:10:15.482 --> 01:10:17.484
<i>You remember this gun?</i>

01:10:18.586 --> 01:10:20.253
<i>When you bought it?</i>

01:10:20.855 --> 01:10:23.925
Eight years, seven months
and 13 days ago.

01:10:25.358 --> 01:10:26.761
The day I quit drinking.

01:10:28.428 --> 01:10:29.864
In case I couldn't hack it.

01:10:31.566 --> 01:10:33.901
[The Associate]
<i>Ruby's life or yours, Tom.</i>

01:10:35.368 --> 01:10:38.806
<i>It's the best I can offer</i>
<i>on such short notice.</i>

01:10:43.845 --> 01:10:45.847
[sobbing]

01:10:50.350 --> 01:10:51.886
At least tell me where she is.

01:10:52.019 --> 01:10:53.654
[The Associate] <i>I would text</i>
<i>you a picture,</i>

01:10:53.788 --> 01:10:56.557
<i>but it's, too dark.</i>

01:10:57.390 --> 01:10:59.594
Just tell me,
I need to know.

01:11:00.427 --> 01:11:02.597
[The Associate] <i>She's buried</i>
<i>in a shallow grave</i>

01:11:02.730 --> 01:11:05.199
<i>at the base of a macadamia tree</i>

01:11:05.432 --> 01:11:07.735
<i>inside a large</i>
<i>green duffle bag.</i>

01:11:07.869 --> 01:11:09.469
[Tom crying]

01:11:10.938 --> 01:11:13.107
<i>You need to make</i>
<i>a decision, Tom.</i>

01:11:13.775 --> 01:11:16.077
How will I know
she's been set free?

01:11:16.443 --> 01:11:17.879
[The Associate] <i>You won't.</i>

01:11:19.446 --> 01:11:20.581
But I still have 10 minutes.

01:11:20.715 --> 01:11:22.282
[The Associate] <i>I'm sorry, Tom.</i>

01:11:22.449 --> 01:11:24.051
<i>I gave you the benefit</i>
<i>of choice</i>

01:11:24.185 --> 01:11:25.318
<i>in the matter.</i>

01:11:25.620 --> 01:11:27.221
- <i>It's out of my hands now.</i>
-No.

01:11:27.922 --> 01:11:29.590
[The Associate] <i>If you'll</i>
<i>excuse me,</i>

01:11:29.724 --> 01:11:32.527
<i>I'm getting called away</i>
<i>to another situation.</i>

01:11:32.660 --> 01:11:34.896
<i>A matter of life or death.</i>

01:11:35.663 --> 01:11:38.566
<i>It's been a pleasure</i>
<i>getting to know you, Tom.</i>

01:11:39.033 --> 01:11:40.768
<i>This concludes</i>
<i>our transaction.</i>

01:11:40.902 --> 01:11:43.538
-No, way, way, wait.
-[telephone disconnecting]

01:12:09.462 --> 01:12:12.033
[instrumental music]

01:12:30.318 --> 01:12:32.119
[gun cocking]

01:12:34.255 --> 01:12:36.791
[screaming]

01:12:53.307 --> 01:12:55.142
[inhales sharply]

01:13:05.353 --> 01:13:07.454
[car window opening]

01:13:10.124 --> 01:13:12.693
[crickets chirping]

01:13:35.049 --> 01:13:37.484
[breathing deeply]

01:13:51.532 --> 01:13:54.068
[distant train horn]

01:14:00.775 --> 01:14:02.410
[Ruby on recording]
<i>My name is Ruby.</i>

01:14:02.910 --> 01:14:06.013
<i>and I'm with my father.</i>

01:14:08.182 --> 01:14:10.518
[car accelerating]

01:14:10.651 --> 01:14:13.888
[intense music]

01:14:17.558 --> 01:14:19.260
Call Emergency Services.

01:14:19.427 --> 01:14:22.129
[automated voice]
<i>Calling Emergency Services.</i>

01:14:23.064 --> 01:14:25.199
-[Abigail] <i>Yes, Tom.</i>
-I've found her.

01:14:25.333 --> 01:14:26.634
Come and get me.

01:14:26.767 --> 01:14:29.704
[intense music]

01:14:33.007 --> 01:14:35.076
[train horn]

01:14:42.917 --> 01:14:45.619
Yeah!

01:14:50.524 --> 01:14:53.027
[car screeching]

01:14:53.361 --> 01:14:56.030
[intense music]

01:15:04.405 --> 01:15:06.807
Ruby, hold on!

01:15:07.675 --> 01:15:09.243
Come on!

01:15:35.603 --> 01:15:37.638
[grunting]

01:15:54.488 --> 01:15:56.490
[phone beeping]

01:15:56.624 --> 01:16:01.629
Ruby!

01:16:20.347 --> 01:16:22.983
[insects trilling]

01:17:16.704 --> 01:17:19.707
[siren blaring at distance]

01:17:22.544 --> 01:17:23.777
Ruby!

01:17:24.011 --> 01:17:25.479
Ruby! Thank God, thank God.

01:17:25.614 --> 01:17:26.814
[police sirens]

01:17:26.947 --> 01:17:28.215
It's okay.

01:17:28.449 --> 01:17:30.117
You're with me now,
it's good.

01:17:31.719 --> 01:17:33.087
Please.

01:17:33.921 --> 01:17:35.557
[cars screeching to halt]

01:17:36.591 --> 01:17:40.728
Please don't make me do it,
not after all that.

01:17:41.596 --> 01:17:43.030
[The Associate] <i>Tom.</i>

01:17:45.399 --> 01:17:46.834
<i>Let Ruby go.</i>

01:17:55.809 --> 01:17:57.244
It's alright.

01:18:02.950 --> 01:18:05.186
[The Associate]
<i>I have excellent news, Tom.</i>

01:18:05.452 --> 01:18:08.956
<i>It appears Ruby is going</i>
<i>to be freed after all.</i>

01:18:09.089 --> 01:18:12.059
-Really?
<i>-Her odds look very good.</i>

01:18:12.193 --> 01:18:14.529
Thank you. Thank you for
saving me from doing that.

01:18:14.663 --> 01:18:15.763
Thank you.

01:18:15.896 --> 01:18:17.431
[The Associate] <i>Ruby negotiated</i>

01:18:17.566 --> 01:18:19.733
<i>her own release, Tom.</i>

01:18:19.934 --> 01:18:21.402
<i>As you know,</i>

01:18:21.636 --> 01:18:22.937
<i>I'm always called in</i>

01:18:23.070 --> 01:18:26.541
<i>on matters of life or death.</i>

01:18:27.007 --> 01:18:29.743
[Terri] <i>Tom,</i>
<i>can you hear me?</i>

01:18:29.910 --> 01:18:31.345
-Terri?
-[Terri] <i>Talk to me, Tom.</i>

01:18:31.513 --> 01:18:33.914
-Terri?
<i>-Tom, you gave me your word.</i>

01:18:34.248 --> 01:18:35.983
[Terri] <i>Please bring her home.</i>

01:18:36.116 --> 01:18:38.152
But I almost made it!
I was close!

01:18:38.285 --> 01:18:41.455
[The Associate] <i>I'm sorry, Tom.</i>
<i>This is out of my purview.</i>

01:18:41.690 --> 01:18:45.326
<i>The agreement was between you</i>
<i>and your ex-wife.</i>

01:18:45.893 --> 01:18:47.361
[Terri] <i>Tom, can you hear me?</i>

01:18:47.696 --> 01:18:48.929
<i>Talk to me, Tom.</i>

01:18:49.296 --> 01:18:51.198
Is Terri real?
Is any of this real?

01:18:51.332 --> 01:18:53.400
[The Associate]
<i>Anything is possible.</i>

01:18:55.302 --> 01:18:56.971
[Terri] <i>Come out</i>
<i>and talk to me, please.</i>

01:18:57.539 --> 01:18:59.608
Please don't make me
go out there and see her, I

01:18:59.840 --> 01:19:02.176
I've broken too many promises
already, she's gonna kill me.

01:19:02.309 --> 01:19:03.911
[The Associate] <i>You've</i>
<i>exceeded the allotted time</i>

01:19:04.044 --> 01:19:05.580
<i>for our discussion, Tom.</i>

01:19:05.980 --> 01:19:08.983
<i>Once again, it's been a</i>
<i>pleasure getting to know you.</i>

01:19:09.116 --> 01:19:10.619
No, no, no, no, no.
Give me one more chance.

01:19:10.851 --> 01:19:13.220
[The Associate] <i>This concludes</i>
<i>our transaction.</i>

01:19:13.555 --> 01:19:14.556
No!

01:19:14.689 --> 01:19:15.956
[police sirens]

01:19:16.357 --> 01:19:17.825
[Abigail on megaphone]
<i>Tom, it's Abigail.</i>

01:19:17.958 --> 01:19:20.361
<i>Put the gun down and come out.</i>

01:19:22.329 --> 01:19:25.866
<i>Tom, put the gun down</i>
<i>and come out.</i>

01:19:38.979 --> 01:19:41.815
[instrumental music]

01:19:42.751 --> 01:19:44.218
You sleep, baby girl.

01:19:44.818 --> 01:19:46.086
I gotta go talk to your mum.

01:19:46.220 --> 01:19:48.590
Make everything alright
like I always do.

01:19:48.723 --> 01:19:49.990
You know how your mum gets.

01:19:50.592 --> 01:19:53.861
[Terri] <i>Tom you gave me</i>
<i>your word remember.</i>

01:19:54.361 --> 01:19:58.132
I promise, I'm gonna make
it better than it was before.

01:19:58.299 --> 01:19:59.833
It's going to be like
none of this ever happened.

01:19:59.967 --> 01:20:01.335
You have my word.

01:20:03.638 --> 01:20:05.039
God is my witness.

01:20:08.677 --> 01:20:09.910
[siren blaring]

01:20:10.077 --> 01:20:11.445
[man 1] Freeze!

01:20:11.579 --> 01:20:12.880
[siren blaring]

01:20:25.025 --> 01:20:28.162
[The Associate] <i>I've enjoyed</i>
<i>our conversation, Ruby.</i>

01:20:29.396 --> 01:20:31.899
[The Associate] <i>It's been</i>
<i>a very pleasant exchange.</i>

01:20:32.032 --> 01:20:33.601
[muffled gunshot]

01:20:35.202 --> 01:20:39.039
<i>This concludes our transaction.</i>

01:20:41.576 --> 01:20:43.844
[muffled gunshot]
